Blanche Forsythe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blanche_Forsythe 0 Blanche Forsythe was a British actress of the silent era. She was born in Islington in the mid 1880s and died in Middlesex in 1953 - aged 80. Blanche_Forsythe was a_British_actress of the_silent_era .
